trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Udostępnia dane dla <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent"> </xref> zdarzeń.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> event is raised by the designer host for certain actions on a control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>Zdarzenie jest wywoływane przez projektanta hosta dla pewne akcje w formancie na powierzchni projektu.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> is handled by a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> delegate method, which takes a ViewEventArgs object as a parameter.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>Jest obsługiwany przez <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler>delegować metody, która przyjmuje obiekt ViewEventArgs jako parametr.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class supplies a default delegate to handle the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>Klasa zapewnia domyślne pełnomocnika, aby obsłużyć <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Custom control designers override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnClick%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnPaint%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner.OnTemplateModeChanged%2A> methods to process those events for the control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Projektanci kontrolki niestandardowej zastępują <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnClick%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnPaint%2A>, i <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner.OnTemplateModeChanged%2A>metody przetwarzania tych zdarzeń formantu na powierzchni projektu.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner.OnTemplateModeChanged%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnPaint%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.OnClick%2A>

trans-unit.source: The designer host initializes a ViewEventArgs object for the type of action on the design surface, and then passes the object to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> delegate.
trans-unit.target: Host projektanta inicjuje obiekt ViewEventArgs dla typu akcji na powierzchni projektu, a następnie przekazuje obiekt do <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler>delegować.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.Region%2A> property represents the control designer region that the event applies to.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.Region%2A>Właściwość reprezentuje obszar projektanta kontroli zdarzenie dotyczy.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.Region%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A> property of the ViewEventArgs object indicates which type of action: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> event.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>Właściwość obiektu ViewEventArgs wskazuje typ akcji: — <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> event.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A> property supplies the event arguments that are specific to the type of action.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A>Właściwości dostarcza argumentów zdarzenia, które są specyficzne dla typu akcji.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, the designer host initializes ViewEventArgs objects as follows: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs> object when you click a region.
trans-unit.target: Na przykład host projektanta inicjuje ViewEventArgs obiektów w następujący sposób: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs>obiektu po kliknięciu region.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PaintEventArgs> object when a control is drawn on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PaintEventArgs>obiekt narysować kontrolkę na powierzchni projektu.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PaintEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateModeChangedEventArgs> object when the template editing mode changes for the control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateModeChangedEventArgs>obiektu, gdy tryb edycji szablonu dla formantu na powierzchni projektu.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateModeChangedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: For more information about events and delegates, see [NIB: Events and Delegates](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d98fd58b-fa4f-4598-8378-addf4355a115).
trans-unit.target: Aby uzyskać więcej informacji o zdarzeniach i delegatów, zobacz [NIB: zdarzenia i delegatów](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d98fd58b-fa4f-4598-8378-addf4355a115).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs"></xref> class for the type of view event on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Inicjuje nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs"> </xref> klasy dla typu widoku zdarzeń na powierzchni projektu.

trans-unit.source: The ViewEventArgs constructor is used by the designer host to initialize a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs> object for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> event.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktor ViewEventArgs jest używany przez hosta projektanta zainicjować <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>obiekt do <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The designer host passes the initialized <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs> object to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> delegate.
trans-unit.target: Zainicjowana klasa przekazuje host projektanta <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>do obiektu <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler>delegować.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventHandler> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Typically, `region` is set for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> events, and `null` (`Nothing` in Visual Basic) for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> events.
trans-unit.target: Zazwyczaj `region` ustawiono dla <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>zdarzenia i `null` (`Nothing` w języku Visual Basic) dla <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>i <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>

trans-unit.source: The type of action that raised the event; used to initialize the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType*>.
trans-unit.target: Typ akcji, który wywołał zdarzenie; używany do inicjowania <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType*>

trans-unit.source: The designer region that the action applies to; used to initialize the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.Region*>.
trans-unit.target: Projektanta regionu, którego dotyczy akcji; używany do inicjowania <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.Region*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.Region*>

trans-unit.source: The event arguments associated with `eventType`; used to initialize the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs*>.
trans-unit.target: Argumenty zdarzeń skojarzonych z `eventType`; używane do zainicjowania <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the event arguments that are associated with the action that raised the event.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera argumenty zdarzeń, które są skojarzone z akcją, który wywołał zdarzenie.

trans-unit.source: The EventArgs property supplies the event arguments that are specific to the type of action that is specified in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Właściwość EventArgs dostarcza argumentów zdarzenia, które są specyficzne dla typu akcji, która została określona w <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>Właściwości.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, when you click a region, the designer host initializes the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A> as a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> event, and then initializes the EventArgs property as a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs> object.
trans-unit.target: Na przykład po kliknięciu obszarem projektanta hosta inicjuje <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>jako <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>zdarzeń, a następnie inicjuje właściwość EventArgs jako <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs>obiektu.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionMouseEventArgs> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventType%2A>

trans-unit.source: Similarly, the designer host initializes the EventArgs property with a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PaintEventArgs> object for a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> event, or a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateModeChangedEventArgs> object for a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Podobnie, host projektanta inicjuje właściwość EventArgs <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PaintEventArgs>obiekt do <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>zdarzenia lub <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateModeChangedEventArgs>obiekt do <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateModeChangedEventArgs> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PaintEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The EventArgs property is initialized by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Właściwość EventArgs jest inicjowana przez <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>konstruktora.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: An EventArgs that contains additional event data that is specific to the type of event.
trans-unit.target: Typ EventArgs, który zawiera dane dodatkowe zdarzenia, które są specyficzne dla typu zdarzenia.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of action that raised the event.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera typ akcji, która wywołała zdarzenie.

trans-unit.source: The EventType property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs> object indicates which type of action raised the event: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> event.
trans-unit.target: Właściwość EventType <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>obiektu wskazuje typ akcji zgłoszone zdarzenie: — <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> event.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A> property supplies the event arguments that are specific to the type of action.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A>Właściwości dostarcza argumentów zdarzenia, które są specyficzne dla typu akcji.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.EventArgs%2A>

trans-unit.source: The EventType property is initialized by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Właściwość EventType jest inicjowany przez <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>konstruktora.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent"></xref> that specifies the type of action that raised the event.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent"> </xref> , który określa typ akcji, która wywołała zdarzenie.

trans-unit.source: Gets the designer region that the event applies to.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera projektanta obszarze, w którym zdarzenie dotyczy.

trans-unit.source: The Region property represents the control designer region that the event applies to.
trans-unit.target: Właściwość Region reprezentuje obszar projektanta kontroli zdarzenie dotyczy.

trans-unit.source: Typically, the Region property is set for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click> events, and `null` (`Nothing` in Visual Basic) for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> events.
trans-unit.target: Zwykle właściwość Region jest ustawiona dla <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>zdarzenia i `null` (`Nothing` w języku Visual Basic) dla <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint>i <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.TemplateModeChanged> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Paint> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEvent.Click>

trans-unit.source: The Region property is initialized by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Właściwości Region jest inicjowany przez <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>konstruktora.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ViewEventArgs.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion"></xref> that the action applies to.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion"> </xref> Stosowanym do akcji.
